

h2 Sign Up
form(class='sign-up')
  div(class='form-group')
    label(for='first-name')
    input(id='first-name' type='text' placeholder='First name')
  div(class='form-group')
    label(for='last-name')
    input(id='last-name' type='text' placeholder='Last name')
  div(class='form-group')
    label(for='username')
    input(id='username' type='text' placeholder='Username')
  include includes/authorization-fields
  button(id='sign-up-button' type='submit') Sign Up
a(href='/log-in') If you already have an account -- log in here.
